{"tid":1408883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷工罷市罷課] 快啲禁入黎睇罷工美食分享","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T00:18:11.000Z","uid":138002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e72d8bc236cc2c68164c5e4ab0fdf39ffe8ef7f","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"好多人好苦惱聽日全部地方罷市點解決食野問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家send俾住七區集會附近嘅居民叫佢地幫幫手<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如果有能力捐野又too long no read嘅可以直接拉落去睇同色title內容，寫左有咩物資可以準備帶出去派</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">出去罷工又窮撚無野捐到嘅各位義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地都有野要帶出去，可以拉低多少少睇同色title嘅字</span><br />\n但係請大家記住！為左令罷工更有效，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日要罷埋市，所以唔可以買開緊嘅商鋪野</span></span> 咁樣只會令同路人覺得少左個商機<br />\n<br />\n<strong>方案一：香港人煮飯仔日</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請各位有cookset/gas爐嘅 帶去七區集會現場<br />\n可以不斷煮定啲野食派街坊<br />\n住係集會地方附近嘅居民都請煮少少野俾大家食<br />\n唔係煮都可以貢獻下屋企雪櫃嘅嘢食<br />\n又可以整多啲冰出黎俾帶手攜雪櫃嘅手足雪野<br />\n一齊圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識到朋友又聽下唔同人對場運動點睇<br />\n<br />\n<strong>方案二：自私食</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位自私撚可以係屋企帶杯面 同 用熱水壺裝水<br />\n甚至可以係屋企可以整熟左啲面<br />\n分開裝多個醬汁，例如豉油、芝麻醬等等<br />\n到時自己整撈面正到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係想睇下現場/街坊會唔會有野食派嘅<br />\n最好就帶多個非即棄食物盒啦 環保撚表示<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">需要大家攞出黎嘅物資</span><br />\n大量嘅容器去裝野食 及 餐具<br />\n杯面 及 熱水<br />\n蛋糕/energy bar等小食<br />\n野飲<br />\nCookset / Gas爐 及 gas<br />\n可以淥熟嘅野食 (用手攜雪櫃放冰裝)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">義士自私準備嘅野</span><br />\n非即棄食物盒 及 餐具<br />\n...以及上面方案二內容的食物<br />\n<br />\n其實社運都可以食得招積，屌狗出色架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令每一個為香港努力貢獻嘅人係平時都要捱苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢場運動帶俾大家嘅更多係香港人嘅愛<br />\n不分化 &middot; 不割蓆 &middot; 不篤灰"},{"pid":"ef6197a9d035d9234d8268e9b5dac539272ac805","tid":1408883,"uid":288417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:39:53.000Z","msg":"招食物idea<br />\n<br />\n我會帶三文治同撈面"},{"pid":"462a376c3808880fd9ecacd43543a6dea7a9759b","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:15:50.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"de5c6011fa2171a0182554b7ece57aae5351a7cd","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:00.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"cfa681668115aa4a57e6d44ccec55261543c5788","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:11.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"dcbf290e181f791eedf470e45834fc3b34a5a134","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"5a459da075d4c04be34b28c837305d7b9c8bd0b7","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"7917280638db0e32f2f1715b20dec79483f070eb","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"e857b625c827191bfc00a4fe6b10a374ad4bf2b6","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:16:58.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"aa84ea2302dc57bf52c4aa0a62857c959f52a416","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:17:16.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"dfc141be2bc8c59c1c4e055ea524a55c8bc1e763","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"6339befe5947af45fab50f99e8f993b90ee14d46","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:17:44.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"84cd300e8f253592cf40a61237e93cca362e1cb2","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"},{"pid":"845ce12304426367b1f46d1b1cc42f613b80338f","tid":1408883,"uid":138002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"一陣七區集會見"}]}